   - **Choosing intersection-over-activity-tags vs Jaccard**: Decided on activity tags as denominator because it rewards users who match all activity tags regardless of how broad their interest list is. Jaccard would unfairly penalize users with many interests.
   - **Rejection return type**: Chose discriminated union over `null`/throwing — null loses the reason, throwing makes the function impure. Union forces compile-time handling.
